{"tid":2031584,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實除咗國安法，今個星期仲發生過咩事？","createTime":"2020-05-23T13:18:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T13:40:50.000Z","uid":83615,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4eb85150804f3e4292d77d9ba97a657380df19","tid":2031584,"uid":83615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:18:35.000Z","msg":"等我話你知：<br />\n<br />\n立法會強行選主席；<br />\n頭條新聞被下架；<br />\n歷史科試題被DQ；<br />\n當然再荒謬都荒謬不過所謂港版國安法。<br />\n<br />\n香港人善忘大家都知，所以小弟整咗條片畀大家回顧下今個星期發生過咩大事，希望大家分享出去，等更多唔睇新聞嘅港豬朋友了解一下今日香港正發生嘅事。<br />\n而大家聽日出之前，亦都可以了解更多議題，對準暴政。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XtMGOgT_k1o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXtMGOgT_k1o&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=405ce127\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XtMGOgT_k1o</a><br />\n勿忘初心，香港加油。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33087094e66c56c3c984e9a0950c6e7d9f116e84","tid":2031584,"uid":348453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0406f65d85eeb3aac723ae6e0e13cc42e81c9c35","tid":2031584,"uid":83615,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:21:07.000Z","msg":"JJ插沙跪求幫忙CLS"},{"pid":"8f5545aec19464e6edcca2f5cc7201803c429aec","tid":2031584,"uid":83615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:21:17.000Z","msg":"JJ插沙跪求幫忙CLS"},{"pid":"af0bb15bd8a356b845aedfbad5db891a5bc2127c","tid":2031584,"uid":83615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:21:27.000Z","msg":"JJ插沙跪求幫忙CLS"},{"pid":"c12dd1599f80ad14e32e0ec69b24cad073cbcc88","tid":2031584,"uid":83615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:21:37.000Z","msg":"JJ插沙跪求幫忙CLS"},{"pid":"03cb9220da216eaf129a68d1d714c42f6d983bea","tid":2031584,"uid":83615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20